  {
    icon: bulletIconSVG,
    text: `Facilitated and lead 5-day design sprint <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-T8F0cJ4rcg" target="_blank">@Valeo CarLab</a> that quickly lead to <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jFQ8wxCANic" target="_blank">Valeo Racer</a>, a new extended reality in-car gaming experience.`
